>http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"驚你睇唔到我留言<br />\n所以quote #1<br />\n好心你集中開一個兔仔post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開十鳩幾個洗走晒寵物台其他動物嘅post<br />\n一係你就去站務台叫admin開個兔仔台畀你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5dfbc750745a493831362e8ddc857c82465063","tid":759281,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e16f7471277beb6823e8777cef85b6bd418119c","tid":759281,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3b4584714326607557864d68b9e76b9fa29fc67","tid":759281,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">這個post 會簡單講述兔子驚慌的時候與牠們視覺的關係。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔正前方是盲點，除了這盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。當牠們側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。大眼睛和大耳朵的構造讓牠們可以偵測到捕獵者(predatory animals)追食。牠們比我們人類看的顏色有限。兔子在大自然內是被補獵的動物(prey animal)，是每個捕獵者(predatory animals)的目標, 沒有自然本能去攻擊他人。(你可想像正前方是盲點，側面才看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）兔子在主人面前會以有限的視角，靈敏的嗅覺、聽覺和觸覺去偵測主人。兔子也有遠視，所以在牠們的視線範圍內走得越遠，牠們就看得越清楚。以下video 可看到主人在牠視線範圍內走得越遠，牠側面看得越清楚然後追着主人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dbce50e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔子驚慌的時候，耳朵會平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。以下圖片可以看到兔子驚慌：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204413_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204413_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg&h=3b795d88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">垂耳兔子驚慌時會耳朵豎起，有時有一點兒向前。以下這張圖片可看到垂耳兔驚慌的時候：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204438_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204438_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg&h=1c25088e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">垂耳兔子舒適時耳朵會放鬆，有時有一點兒向後。以下2張圖片可看到垂耳兔舒適的時候：</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204507_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204507_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg&h=403b9772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/204507_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F204507_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg&h=f71b14cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔子驚慌時會通常用靈敏的嗅覺和聽覺向前探索一下，當敵人就快殺到過來的時候，牠會側面(即是正面)睇實然後逃去。當然在大自然內如果敵人高速殺過來，牠會立刻逃走。以下3個videos 可以看到這個驚慌時的步驟：<br />\n可在0:34看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/edRn4kQRKmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FedRn4kQRKmU&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=630d7c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/edRn4kQRKmU</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">可在0:29看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6G6WQiL_SV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6G6WQiL_SV8&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f2dc96d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6G6WQiL_SV8</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">可在0:38看到</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EQgigVs15dQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEQgigVs15dQ&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2e56df00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EQgigVs15dQ</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>更多關於兔子驚慌的身體語言：</strong><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5c7a1acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:40:33.000Z","msg":"驚你睇唔到我留言<br />\n所以quote #1<br />\n好心你集中開一個兔仔post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開十鳩幾個洗走晒寵物台其他動物嘅post<br />\n一係你就去站務台叫admin開個兔仔台畀你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬隻耳仔平放左在後面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8330cf7afada3969fceac94a817bf47158219f9c","tid":759281,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西，兔子也有遠視。以下video 也可以看到兔子驚慌：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7x6ANuo5m6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7x6ANuo5m6E&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0bev1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=4120bc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7x6ANuo5m6E</a>"},{"pid":"3310abe05b3f86fa7de4886521cfd6dac3679fe1","tid":759281,"uid":114079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一睇就知係專制毒撚黎<br />\n開口埋口都兔仔 屌你個腦都係兔腦黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431149df3dc82ec6e8c2e00d2b40cb78dca3b06e","tid":759281,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3310abe05b3f86fa7de4886521cfd6dac3679fe1","tid":759281,"uid":114079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一睇就知係專制毒撚黎<br />\n開口埋口都兔仔 屌你個腦都係兔腦黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:51:03.000Z","msg":"佢係咪驚畀人再喺寵物台開post屌佢廢老<br />\n所以而家唔開新post<br />\n用返舊post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}